    • SteadyStateGAWithStrongElitism

      public int[][] SteadyStateGAWithStrongElitism (SolutionPop problem, int p1_index, int p2_index, int[] c1_solution, int[] c2_solution, double[] child_memeplex)

      Replaces worst 2 of a population with the best 2 out of parent and child solutions.

      Parameters:
      problem - Used to get information from the population, as well as to set the values of memeplexes.
      p1_index - Index of parent 1 in the population.
      p2_index - Index of parent 2 in the population.
      c1_solution - Binary representation of child 1 solution.
      c2_solution - Binary representation of child 2 solution.
      child_memeplex - Memeplex shared by child solutions.
      Returns:
      new population after replacement has been applied.
